<view class="container">
	<view class="logo">
		<image src="../images/instructions/neimeng/step1.png" mode="widthFix"></image>
	</view>
	<view class="title">1.拭擦安装位置</view>
	<view class="sub-title">
		<view>请用湿纸巾将安装处进行擦拭，</view>
		<view>再用干纸巾将水分擦干</view>
	</view>
	<view class="logo">
		<image src="../images/instructions/neimeng/step2.png" mode="widthFix"></image>
	</view>
	<view class="title">2.将设备安装到指定位置</view>
	<view class="sub-title">
		<view>撕开设备背面的胶纸，将设备紧贴在车辆</view>
		<view>后视镜正后方的挡风玻璃上</view>
	</view>
	<view class="tips">
		<view class="label">注意：</view>
		<view>
			<view>禁止将设备安装在非申办车辆上！</view>
			<view>激活后请勿移动设备，否则无法正常使用！</view>
		</view>
	</view>
	<view class="btn" catchtap="handleGo">设备已安装，下一步</view>
</view>
